{"tid":1372403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我決定第日個廢老退左休我係唔撚會比錢養佢","createTime":"2019-07-27T12:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T08:19:44.000Z","uid":261961,"like":112,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ef21b1ad757a8a5050367065c3e128e15124d8","tid":1372403,"uid":261961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"我老豆係個的士狗<br />\n本來6月個時嘈左次大既就開始冇同佢講野<br />\n唔知我老豆老母係弱智定係乜野<br />\n好似到而家先恍然大悟知我咩立場<br />\n呢個月都平平靜靜一句野都冇同佢講過<br />\n到左前日, 個廢老老豆就開始挑戰我底線<br />\n食飯個時轉左個電視去CCTVB新聞台. (本來呢個月以黎都係播東張西望)<br />\n佢仲要開到老撚咁大聲係到踩我底線..<br />\n<br />\n到左頭先食飯又係到屌<br />\n又話出面 &quot;暴動&quot; 搞到佢個死的士狗今日冇生意<br />\n成家又係到你一句佢一句咁. 個犬儒老母又係到認同個的士狗<br />\n <br />\n我決定左我都要行動升級<br />\n我決定左唔再同個的士狗一齊食飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁撚叻就叫共產黨養你兩個死廢老<br />\n睇下你幾時訓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae69ce526a7c829b3e9f3a8be377d7589fb68f7","tid":1372403,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:12:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9eafd4b41243f676ef22da76ef3b44f88d9e5ac5","tid":1372403,"uid":181778,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30a05ce2512c0196a43df9981f95f10ca0df2153","tid":1372403,"uid":261961,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"9eafd4b41243f676ef22da76ef3b44f88d9e5ac5","tid":1372403,"uid":181778,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a